1-- when we have to align items more like upar logo hai uske neeche text toh usme hume 2 class to define krne hi hai dono
mei display :flex krna hai kyuki text ko logo ke centre krne ke liye.
also isme bhi minimum width btate hai for justify content se space dete hai nhi toh text chipke chipke hote hai

 2 -- also jaise kbhi search bar bna rhe hai toh usme minimum width define krte hai take aise pura bar dikhe
nhi toh chota reh jata hai

3-- try to class differently in div like agr ek class mei saari images hai for same thing then un image ko 
bhi ek class mei krokyuki overall wali se hum flex wrap aur space decide kr skte hai particular image wali se 
hum width height decide kr skte hai

4-- jo footer container humne bnaya usme agr hum flex direction ko column krenge toh usme koi bhi cheez daalenge 
toh column wise aayega isliye usme column nhi krna hai jo hum items likhne hai specifically usme column krna hai nhi toh
side by side 2 column nhi dikha payenge

5-- Use position: relative on the outer box and position: absolute , top: 50% left: 50% , transform: translate(-50%, -50%) on the inner text box to center it perfectly over an image. (to write text over image requirements)

6--when u have to make a toggle like click on one box and checkbox opens with extended content then we use type=checkbox and 
label it with id
